42194f26-e326-11ec-8fea-0242ac121232.title: DONE TO INITIAL COMMIT
42194f26-e326-11ec-8fea-0242ac121232.description:
Done to Commit Ratio = Delivered Points / Commit Points

Delivered points also known as Velocity is the sum of story points (final estimate) of all the tasks completed within a sprint.

Commit Points are the number of story points a team planned to deliver at the beginning of the sprint. Commit Points is the sum of story points for all the tickets in the sprint backlog at the sprint start time.

5ad82dba-e322-11ec-8fea-0242ac121232.title: UNPLANNED ADDED (CREEP)
5ad82dba-e322-11ec-8fea-0242ac121232.description: Creep to Commit Ratio = Creep Points / Commit Points Creep Points are the number of points of all the tickets added to the sprint after the sprint start time. Commit Points are the number of story points a team planned to deliver at the beginning of the sprint. Commit Points are the sum of story points of all the tickets in the sprint backlog at the sprint start time.

91997098-da67-11ec-9d64-0242ac121232.title: SPRINT PREDICTABILITY
91997098-da67-11ec-9d64-0242ac121232.description: This is the Standard Deviation on Sprint Velocity. Deviation percentage between 0-15% shows that the team is committing and delivering a uniform and predictable number of story points.

919973d6-da67-11ec-9d64-0242ac121232.title: SPRINT VELOCITY
919973d6-da67-11ec-9d64-0242ac121232.description: Average Story Points delivered over the specified time range.
